ng to our model and discuss their\ncompatibility with observations. In addition, we improve the analytical\nrelations between the plateau luminosity and plateau duration to the properties\nof the pre-explosion progenitor (Arnett 1980; Popov 1993).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 25 Apr 2014 04:11:52 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-28"}
